Fabregas to Sign Five-Season Barcelona Contract, Vanguardia Says

-- B y   S h a r o n   S m y t h
-- 
2011-08-13T07:41:05Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-13/fabregas-to-sign-five-season-barcelona-contract-vanguardia-says.html
Arsenal captain Cesc Fabregas will
travel to  Barcelona  today or tomorrow to sign with Barcelona,  La
Vanguardia  reported, without citing anyone.  Fabregas will sign a five-season contract with the club and
may be officially presented to fans on Aug. 15, the Barcelona-
based newspaper said.  The player, who debuted with Arsenal at just 16 years of
age, will be sold for 34 million euros ($48 million) plus a
possible six extra variable payments, the newspaper added
without specifying to what those payments would be linked.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Sharon Smyth in Madrid at 
 ssmyth2@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Andrew Blackman at   ablackman@bloomberg.net  